Package org.orderManagement.dataAccess

Class AbstractDAO<T>

java.lang.Object
org.orderManagement.dataAccess.AbstractDAO<T>
Type Parameters:
T - -placeholder object (Could be a Client/Product/Order)
Direct Known Subclasses:
ClientDAO, OrderDAO, ProductDAO
public class AbstractDAO<T>
extends java.lang.Object
Class for implementing some reflexive methods The idea of this class is to create methods that can be used for all objects
